it is a puja for a new beginning like building a new house or a wedding
what is the importance of the pichhaura
it is a traditional garment worn by married women during auspicious ceremonies
it is a very long and difficult pilgrimage that happens only once in twelve years
what is the significance of the four horned ram in the raj jat
that ram leads the procession and it is believed goddess nandas spirit travels with it
what is hill jatra
