whose story is enacted in hill jatra
it depicts scenes of paddy transplantation and pastoral life with a character named lakhya bhoot
bhumiyal is the god of the land worshipped to protect the boundaries of the village
do different villages have different customs for the same festival
yes there are slight differences from village to village but the main spirit is the same
