they will be just like our friendship forever
i packed the churkani dal for you you like it a lot
thank you mother i will miss the food you cook so much
will you be able to cook for yourself there
i will have to learn now i am a married woman
who will i fight with now over silly things
you can fight with me on the phone i won't mind
