of course i will i will wear the pichhaura at every festival with pride
that's my girl don't let the city change you
the mountains are in my blood they can never change
now that you're leaving who will help me with the cows
brother you have to learn all the work now you are the man of the house
you are brave you will manage everything
i'm looking at our childhood photo we look so funny
